{"tid":1384741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人考慮去港交所請願","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:55:48.000Z","uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c6ff5a775d7bd801b47b2a32fe21a3d7744fd8","tid":1384741,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"好明顯依家港共已經係唔會理民意，甚至民生<br />\n係民居射催淚彈佢地都唔會care。不合作運動你d 公司搵少左錢唔會care。香港經濟林唔會care。商會開口佢都唔會care。<br />\n要同港共討價還價只可以係佢地有利益既位出發。大陸利用香港搵錢既途徑，其中一個就係股票市場，如果好多人係平日去港交所請願，相信影響會比所有其他野為大。<br />\n<br />\n記得要和平理性，阻到人番工就唔好。"},{"pid":"dd7b4463a7acc0696fd4feeb6ad37c3dfc68d026","tid":1384741,"uid":6293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:02.000Z","msg":"未電腦化就有用..."},{"pid":"8cf92faed7c5683cd1aa6191a9658eeea82717a4","tid":1384741,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd7b4463a7acc0696fd4feeb6ad37c3dfc68d026","tid":1384741,"uid":6293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:02.000Z","msg":"未電腦化就有用..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"因為未試過所以唔知道，但電腦化左都要有人係現場番工mon 住？<br />\n如果唔係，平時打風都可以開市"},{"pid":"b32105baa71a36f71aacee26dad9af9445ef91bd","tid":1384741,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c362a4d14dfda42b68c3a03844d89982a3c27e","tid":1384741,"uid":38237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span></span>"}]}